          "title": "مثال -13-",
          "problem": "إذا كانت $f(x)=|x|$ فأوجد $\\int_{-3}^4 f(x)dx$",
          "solution": [
            "$f$ دالة مستمرة على $[-3,4]$ ولها قاعدتان هما :",
            "$f(x) = \\\\begin{cases} x \\\\quad, \\\\quad \\\\forall x \\\\ge 0 \\\\\\\\ -x \\\\quad, \\\\quad \\\\forall x < 0 \\\\end{cases}$",
            "$\\therefore \\\\int_{-3}^4 f(x)dx = \\\\int_{-3}^0 (-x)dx + \\\\int_0^4 xdx = [\\\\frac{-x^2}{2}]_{-3}^0 + [\\\\frac{x^2}{2}]_0^4$",
            "$= [0 - (\\\\frac{-(-3)^2}{2})] + [\\\\frac{4^2}{2} - 0] = [0 + \\\\frac{9}{2}] + [\\\\frac{16}{2} - 0] = \\\\frac{9}{2} + \\\\frac{16}{2} = \\\\frac{25}{2}$"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "title": "مثال -14-",
          "problem": "إذا كانت $f(x) = \\\\begin{cases} 2x+1 \\\\quad, \\\\quad x \\\\ge 1 \\\\\\\\ 3 \\\\quad, \\\\quad x < 1 \\\\end{cases}$ فأوجد $\\int_0^5 f(x)dx$",
          "solution": [
            "$f$ مستمرة على الفترة $[0,5]$ وذلك لأنها :",
            "مستمرة عند $x=1$ لأن :",
            "(i) $f(1)=2(1)+1=3$",
            "(ii) $\\lim_{x\\\\rightarrow 1} f(x) = \\\\begin{cases} \\\\lim_{x\\\\rightarrow 1^-} (2x+1) = 2(1)+1=3 = L_1 \\\\\\\\ \\\\lim_{x\\\\rightarrow 1^+} 3 = 3 = L_2 \\\\end{cases}$",
            "$\\therefore L_1=L_2 \\\\quad \\\\therefore \\\\lim_{x\\\\rightarrow 1} f(x)=3$ موجودة $\\\\Rightarrow f(x)=f(1)$",
            "كذلك الدالة مستمرة على كل من $\{x: x < 1\}$ , $\{x: x > 1\}$ ومما أن الدالة مستمرة على $[0,5]$",
            "$\\therefore \\\\int_0^5 f(x)dx = \\\\int_0^1 f(x)dx + \\\\int_1^5 f(x)dx$",
            "$= \\\\int_0^1 3dx + \\\\int_1^5 (2x+1)dx = [3x]_0^1 + [x^2+x]_1^5$",
            "$= [3-0] + [(25+5)-(2)] = 3+28 = 31$"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
